item.title: How do i put in client.java
item.dc:creator: @Graham Graham
item.description:
@Graham wrote:

Download one from another client. They are pretty similar anyway. If a server doesn’t have one you will lose most of the functionality - most of the game logic is done in the client class (poor coding style…).
